<item>
            <title>[LU-17245] lfs utils: misleading error messages when using multiple paths</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17245</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using some lfs utils with multiple paths, and one of the paths has an error, it is possible to get misleading error messages:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-bash&quot;&gt;
$ mkdir /mnt/lustre/d 

$ lfs find /mnt/lustre/typo /mnt/lustre/d
/mnt/lustre/d
lt-lfs: failed &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote-red&quot;&gt;&apos;/mnt/lustre/typo&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: Success&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-bash&quot;&gt;
$ lfs getstripe /mnt/lustre/typo /mnt/lustre/d 
lt-lfs: getstripe &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote-red&quot;&gt;&apos;/mnt/lustre/d&apos;&lt;/span&gt; failed: No such file or directory
/mnt/lustre/d
stripe_count: &#160;1 stripe_size: &#160; 4194304 pattern: &#160; &#160; &#160; 0 stripe_offset: -1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
